Generate Unique CRM Analytics Dashboard Layouts for Different Devices

If multiple layouts are defined for a dashboard, CRM Analytics chooses the optimal layout when displaying the dashboard on a device. To determine the optimal layout, CRM Analytics uses the device properties specified for each layout.

CRM Analytics uses the following rules:

* A layout is eligible if the device meets all its device properties.
* If multiple layouts are eligible, use the one with the most set properties. If tied, use the most recently defined layout.
* If no layouts meet the criteria, use the first defined layout.
title: Choosing Device Layout in CRM Analytics
